    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Voxel Project offers an immersive sandbox experience set in a fully destructible voxel environment. Explore a dynamic world teeming with vehicles, dynamic fire mechanics, enemy NPCs, voxel gore, weapon customization, and a bunch of additional features to discover.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sandbox Mode</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock boundless creativity with unrestricted access to props and weapons, all with unlimited ammo. Explosives, guns, cars, props, NPCs, etc. Utilize your tablet to spawn and manipulate elements, toggling between day and night settings or turning off the NPC AI to prevent them from moving</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148280/extras/796e0c33b1c203dffa6b7acc682d1652.poster.avif?t=1728918108\" width=400 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148280/extras/796e0c33b1c203dffa6b7acc682d1652.webm?t=1728918108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148280/extras/796e0c33b1c203dffa6b7acc682d1652.mp4?t=1728918108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Vehicles</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Voxel project features completely destructible vehicles. Cut off the roof with a plasma saber and make a convertible. Tie objects or ragdolls to the car and drag them across the map.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148280/extras/e2162e5cb5b607412b7dd6cb9cccf199.poster.avif?t=1728918108\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148280/extras/e2162e5cb5b607412b7dd6cb9cccf199.webm?t=1728918108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148280/extras/e2162e5cb5b607412b7dd6cb9cccf199.mp4?t=1728918108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Fire</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set everything on fire and watch it burn, or try to extinguish it to save what’s left</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148280/extras/9bf3957bf1e69febb9d9a381d146343a.poster.avif?t=1728918108\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148280/extras/9bf3957bf1e69febb9d9a381d146343a.webm?t=1728918108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148280/extras/9bf3957bf1e69febb9d9a381d146343a.mp4?t=1728918108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Physics Gun</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manipulate objects using physics-based interactions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148280/extras/a29ea519243314bb24758862c33b6873.poster.avif?t=1728918108\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148280/extras/a29ea519243314bb24758862c33b6873.webm?t=1728918108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148280/extras/a29ea519243314bb24758862c33b6873.mp4?t=1728918108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Voxel Gore</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Demolish ragdolls down to the last voxel</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148280/extras/4313e36abb0c9663b37667c50b95c7ba.poster.avif?t=1728918108\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148280/extras/4313e36abb0c9663b37667c50b95c7ba.webm?t=1728918108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148280/extras/4313e36abb0c9663b37667c50b95c7ba.mp4?t=1728918108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Weapon Customization</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Modify weapons with attachments</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148280/extras/0473c82815691f76dbd10f013a61c91b.poster.avif?t=1728918108\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148280/extras/0473c82815691f76dbd10f013a61c91b.webm?t=1728918108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148280/extras/0473c82815691f76dbd10f013a61c91b.mp4?t=1728918108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And much more features that will be added in the future with updates!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trailer Song: 1$K1 - GODSLAYER [NCS Release]</p>",
